t: We only sent before you Ë¹O ProphetËº men inspired by Us from among the people of each society. Have the deniers not travelled through the land to see what was the end of those Ë¹destroyedËº before them? And surely the Ë¹eternalËº Home of the Hereafter is far better for those mindful Ë¹of AllahËº. Will you not then understand